{"tid":1431851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府除左玩抹黑分化，仲玩左一種手段 一倒果為因","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:42:28.000Z","uid":120377,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b2bf15e2f1d13153c7254d8277fc997c5cea24","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"政府不停想令中間派離開我地，所以不停話我地暴徒，用我地既行動屈我地主動出擊。<br />\n<br />\n班豬好快會相信政府，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">街坊慢慢變做憎黑警，唔係政府</span>，而政府同中聯辦話可以搞獨立調查會，就係要令班豬滿足，解決左佢地既憂慮，佢地就會同我地割席什至幫政府。<br />\n<br />\n而家佢再打多一針，就係話叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地先停手，政府先可以做野</span></span><br />\n代入班豬既世界，佢地會諗:我憎黑警姐，政府無影響我，你地快d停手，等政府做委員會lo。<br />\n佢地既憂慮就會無野<br />\n<br />\n有人會話，咁多野發生左，d人仲可以當無事？仲支持政府？<br />\n<br />\n但777無出過聲，所有野都係黑警做，<span style=\"color: red;\">班豬會覺得解決左黑警就可以。</span><br />\n<br />\n但大家都知，淨係獨立調查委員會係無用，咁多個委員會有邊個成功將班狗官治罪？<br />\n所以五大訴求，缺一不可，要一齊實行<br />\n<br />\n再者，我地要出黎係因為政府，而家要我地停先？點解唔係政府做野先？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">動亂因你而起，你唔搞掂佢，仲叫我地停手？<br />\n我屌你老母呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n倒果為因，混淆視聽，政府一定唔會守信用。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地唔可以比佢地成功，要令大眾有邏輯思考，知道事實真相，文宣要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大力宣傳我地既訴求，事件起因同埋政府悪行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n加油呀大家！"},{"pid":"6b5bd36abbb475ce8ede7e867e79649c764caf8d","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08757feaac3dddefeedbdc6e91ff8b3cca86e967","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d96933a6e5897f6af32f698ba19cd46dbca4e935","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca8a9308849a7096a0293f113015e617373ab2a0","tid":1431851,"uid":231909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"借個位,提提你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=aab03643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp7KMz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp7KMz5.png&h=1dddb453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出黎嬴翻香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"292cfb5a6270fb8694f17094ed3b6bc0f0f73482","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8b9276c83adb986e7d3df4e96b885788d7e91f94","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5585cb2f75705d7ccf9ef8525217b7a97b41018f","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d790c6299f7fd5aa373eb9bcb3abb15136bb4d9","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48087268ef45deff88d907b97f61d17fa08565d0","tid":1431851,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"藍絲洗腦 毒害老中一輩 可以點拆<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431537</a>"},{"pid":"011f6cb0642ac8c6f67a7d00f5962dc1e18e9d8f","tid":1431851,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"岩啊佢老母倒轉黎講"},{"pid":"a5813870cbd962aa702fb4e6275a65223c6d1f37","tid":1431851,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91e5430d0f5199a283a5718bdacda26303fb6498","tid":1431851,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011f6cb0642ac8c6f67a7d00f5962dc1e18e9d8f","tid":1431851,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":